Kentucky's Bluegrass Country leave Lexington on Oct. 16 and 23.
Cycling is on traffic-free back roads with gentle terrain for riders
of any ability. Participants stop at Kentucky Horse Park and Shaker
Village in Pleasant Hill, and tour Harrodsburg, Kentucky's oldest
town. Participants spend nights in antique-furnished inns along the
