</P>
<P>
A six-day, land-based eclipse-viewing trip to Bolivia leaves Miami
for La Paz on Oct. 31. Tour members stay at a downtown hotel in the
Bolivian capital and take leisurely tours of the city including the
Witches' Market. An all-night train trip to the ``center line'' of the
