<TEXT>
<P>
Final count on the fall schedule changes -- 22½ hours of new
programs, including l5 dramas, 13 situation comedies and one
newsmagazine. NBC is replacing seven hours, Fox six, CBS five and ABC
four. All but Fox, which airs just 15 hours a week, carry 22 hours of
primetime a week.
</P>
