In ROSTY (Eaton Ostrow, Times), insert after 9th graf (adding 
 Justice Department investigation of Rostenkowski) xxx of office. 
</P>
<P>
The Justice Department has been investigating allegations
Rostenkowski abused office and campaign accounts by, among other
things, receiving money improperly from the House post office, hiring
workers who did not work, and making improper furniture and gift
purchases with office funds.
</P>
