as in barbecued beef tenderloin, stuffed turkey breast, marinated leg
of lamb, grilled salmon roast, or grilled-smoked ham. 1,250 words, by
Karol V. Menzie (Sun). With GRILL-RECIPES and GRILL-TIPS.

