<HEADLINE>
 Toronto Festival Explores 40 Cultures 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Join the caravan -- and explore 40 cultures without leaving Toronto
 -- at the 26th annual Festival Caravan, June 17-25.
</P>
<P>
