pavilions all over the city. A Caravan passport, available at any Bank
of Montreal branch or at some Bell Phonecentres, includes a map of the
pavilions but not transportation; cost is about $5 U.S. per person per
day, about $10 for a nine-day pass (kids 12 and under are admitted
free with an adult). Information: (416) 977-0466.
